=> Deployment Guide

 1. Local Setup:

Step 1:pip install -r requirements.txt
]Step 2:uvicorn backend.main:app --reload
Open:http://localhost:8000/docs


2. Production Deployment:

Option 1: Docker
i) Create Dockerfile
ii) Expose port 8000

Option 2: Cloud VM
i) AWS EC2
ii) Azure VM
iii) GCP Compute Engine


3. Performance Recommendations:

i) Use GPU for embeddings
ii) Switch to FAISS IVF for large scale
iii) Use Redis cache for session storage
iv) Persist vector index to disk


4. Scaling Strategy:

For multi-user systems:
i) Partition vector index by user
ii) Use distributed vector DB
iii) Add load balancer
